# Testing Standards

- Use Jest for unit tests.
- Test names should describe expected behavior (not implementation details).
- Keep tests deterministic; do not rely on network calls or system time without mocks.
- For behavior changes, add or update tests unless explicitly skipped with justification.
- Ensure test changes pass with `npm test`.
